Class Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.Profile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Profile
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A class representing the fields of a User object that are visible to other users. Implements Serializable and has a field for the serial version.
    Version:
    2.0 - 31.05.21
    Author:
